## Key Discovery: High Variance
- Same seed can score 0.00 or 11.68 on different runs
- Game has internal randomness beyond the seed
- Wipeouts occur when ALL agents hit hp=0 from step 100
- Best strategy: maximize avg across many seeds, accept variance

